OL,3,CGroup sentenced after 'disgraceful'
OL,4,Csexual abuse of family dog
OL,6,FTwo men and a woman have been
OL,7,Fsentenced for a series of sexual
OL,8,Foffences, including actions described
OL,9,Fas "disgraceful" as they sexually
OL,10,Fabused a dog.
OL,12,FGuernsey Magistrate's Court heard how
OL,13,FPeter Leigh, 73, Ian Chatting-Tonks,
OL,14,F63, and Elaine Pasquier, 67, filmed
OL,15,Fthe incident using two cameras on 4
OL,16,FSeptember 2018.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
