FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772399158
OL,3,CGroup sentenced after 'disgraceful'
OL,4,Csexual abuse of family dog
OL,6,FThey forced the dog, which belonged to
OL,7,FChatting-Tonks, to undertake various
OL,8,Fsexual acts, which were said to have
OL,9,Fcaused "visible signs of emotional and
OL,10,Fpsychological distress" to the canine.
OL,12,FLeigh, whose behaviour was described
OL,13,Fas "utterly deviant" by Judge
OL,14,FCatherine Fooks, was sentenced to two
OL,15,Fyears and 10 weeks in prison.
OL,17,FThe other two defendants were given
OL,18,Fcommunity service orders - Chatting-
OL,19,FTonks will undertake 220 hours, while
OL,20,FPasquier received 170 hours.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772399158
OL,3,CGroup sentenced after 'disgraceful'
OL,4,Csexual abuse of family dog
OL,6,FAll three pleaded guilty to all
OL,7,Foffences.
OL,9,FCrown Advocate Chris Dunford for the
OL,10,Fprosecution told the court how the
OL,11,FStates Vet had inspected the abuse
OL,12,Fvideos to understand the psychological
OL,13,Feffect on the dog.
OL,15,FAll three Defence Advocates spoke of
OL,16,Fhow their clients felt ashamed and
OL,17,Fembarrassed by the revelations.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
