OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772399158
OL,3,CGroup sentenced after 'disgraceful'
OL,4,Csexual abuse of family dog
OL,6,FDefending Leigh, Advocate Peter
OL,7,FFerbrache explained how the group
OL,8,Farranged to have sex amongst
OL,9,Fthemselves and any sexual contact with
OL,10,Fthe dog was not pre-planned.
OL,12,FHe described Leigh as having "liberal
OL,13,Fand unusual sexual predilections", but
OL,14,Fstated that some of his client's
OL,15,Factions were not illegal.
OL,17,FAdvocate Sam Steele, defending
OL,18,FChatting-Tonks, described it as a
OL,19,F"distorted sexual experiment" and said
OL,20,Fit was an isolated incident.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
