OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772399158
OL,3,CGroup sentenced after 'disgraceful'
OL,4,Csexual abuse of family dog
OL,6,FAdvocate Amy Davies, defending
OL,7,FPasquier, said her client felt
OL,8,F"victimised" as she was not aware the
OL,9,Fvideo would be kept.
OL,11,FIn a separate hearing at the Royal
OL,12,FCourt, Crown Advocate Dunford
OL,13,Fexplained how videos and messages were
OL,14,Ffound on Leigh's devices following an
OL,15,Funrelated phone search.
OL,17,FThis included the video relating to
OL,18,FChatting-Tonks' dog.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
