PN,38406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772399158
OL,3,CGroup sentenced after 'disgraceful'
OL,4,Csexual abuse of family dog
OL,6,FIn November 2017, Leigh had sent a
OL,7,Fseparate video of a woman having
OL,8,Fsexual intercourse with a Great Dane
OL,9,Fdog to a female friend alongside the
OL,10,Fcaption, "Thought you may enjoy".
OL,12,FHis device also revealed messages
OL,13,Fbetween him and Chatting-Tonks.
OL,15,FThese included naked photos of a
OL,16,Fconsenting 16-year-old girl, which
OL,17,FLeigh took himself whilst on a boat
OL,18,Ftrip with her in 2005.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772399158
OL,3,CGroup sentenced after 'disgraceful'
OL,4,Csexual abuse of family dog
OL,6,FIn June 2024, Chatting-Tonks engaged
OL,7,Fin conversation with the woman, asking
OL,8,Fher, "I've seen photos of you on the
OL,9,Fboat. Do you want them?"
OL,11,FHe also sent her an unsolicited photo
OL,12,Fof his penis.
OL,14,FBoth Leigh and Chatting-Tonks pleaded
OL,15,Fguilty to all offences, including
OL,16,Fbreaking animal welfare law and
OL,17,Ftelecommunications offences.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
