FL,385,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1772399158
OL,3,CGroup sentenced after 'disgraceful'
OL,4,Csexual abuse of family dog
OL,6,FLeigh and Pasquier also admitted to
OL,7,Ftwo separate counts of behaving in an
OL,8,Findecent manner, where they were seen
OL,9,Fengaging in sexual acts in public, in
OL,10,Fa car park in St Peter Port and at
OL,11,FPetit Bot.
OL,13,FIn her sentencing remarks, Judge Fooks
OL,14,Fsaid that they all shared similar
OL,15,Ftastes and had "blurred sexual
OL,16,Fboundaries".
OL,18,FAlongside their individual sentences,
OL,19,Fall three have been disqualified from
OL,20,Fowning a dog for the next decade.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/8
